{"tid":1766711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有烏克蘭前民兵嚟香港視察，被懷疑係新納粹分子，如今已fc確定唔係，請手足切勿炒車","createTime":"2019-12-02T20:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T02:37:12.000Z","uid":79724,"like":437,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"802372836f63a31a3e2ec31a4df651793fee32a1","tid":1766711,"uid":79724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T20:50:01.000Z","msg":"之前個炒車post我開嘅<br />\n冇睇過就唔使搵啦<br />\n<br />\n總之長話短說就係賀幾位烏克蘭嘅前民兵嚟香港視察<br />\n表示支持<br />\n因為身上面嘅紋身令人聯想到納粹<br />\n我就衝出嚟柒叫手足唔好近佢哋<br />\n<br />\n以下係Free Hong Kong Center嘅澄清<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ufhkc/photos/a.468815556801405/1009071022775853/?type=3&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARCl1RYItmITB9Gza5RFhXPAjC5CNHjFxRD_K4dfAxXEo7nRT1SzMKZ-jMgSDu73MCACiIgGNwUEAcfgZ-LgGaSATMmRV7fUMgsR1W6inFV5liVBLyCzbTespyvOdFfhDNsTPMl-mjjJTTdTj0yTxSL6TL0bSIdCOZrwec25-nXzVgUuijjgnL_qENa1LxjRpVV8AZthKUexBdLNx5oTuin9_lZ90mHU8tktOziDq9kV-JdC3DOWaVkNycMFYwgYaziw40_LyUMQWQh3jMmwRVl1wLPQ4W7EiGHIdeFl-UGSsueupdjp11Wjt4oui8d_DhUs1gY_O40-vL1M9TgE8xYUbw&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fufhkc%2Fphotos%2Fa.468815556801405%2F1009071022775853%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26__xts__%255B0%255D%3D68.ARCl1RYItmITB9Gza5RFhXPAjC5CNHjFxRD_K4dfAxXEo7nRT1SzMKZ-jMgSDu73MCACiIgGNwUEAcfgZ-LgGaSATMmRV7fUMgsR1W6inFV5liVBLyCzbTespyvOdFfhDNsTPMl-mjjJTTdTj0yTxSL6TL0bSIdCOZrwec25-nXzVgUuijjgnL_qENa1LxjRpVV8AZthKUexBdLNx5oTuin9_lZ90mHU8tktOziDq9kV-JdC3DOWaVkNycMFYwgYaziw40_LyUMQWQh3jMmwRVl1wLPQ4W7EiGHIdeFl-UGSsueupdjp11Wjt4oui8d_DhUs1gY_O40-vL1M9TgE8xYUbw%26__tn__%3D-R&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=b7d1ecaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ufhkc/photos/a.468815556801405/1009071022775853/?type=3&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARCl1RYItmITB9Gza5RFhXPAjC5CNHjFxRD_K4dfAxXEo7nRT1SzMKZ-jMgSDu73MCACiIgGNwUEAcfgZ-LgGaSATMmRV7fUMgsR1W6inFV5liVBLyCzbTespyvOdFfhDNsTPMl-mjjJTTdTj0yTxSL6TL0bSIdCOZrwec25-nXzVgUuijjgnL_qENa1LxjRpVV8AZthKUexBdLNx5oTuin9_lZ90mHU8tktOziDq9kV-JdC3DOWaVkNycMFYwgYaziw40_LyUMQWQh3jMmwRVl1wLPQ4W7EiGHIdeFl-UGSsueupdjp11Wjt4oui8d_DhUs1gY_O40-vL1M9TgE8xYUbw&amp;__tn__=-R</a><br />\n<br />\nThe statement of the Free Hong Kong Center on the visit of Ukrainian guys to Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDuring the week, we are getting messages about the visit of the small group of young Ukrainian guys to Hong Kong. Some of them are with the question &ldquo;Are the guys involved in far-right movements?&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\nTo clarify all these issues we contacted representatives of the &ldquo;Gonor&rdquo; group. And got quite comprehensive answers.<br />\n<br />\nThese people are really activists of the Revolution of Dignity and as well as veterans of the defending war with Russia. Almost 6 years ago, during the first period of the war, they were connected to the Azov group. However, since 2015 are simple activists, currently countering police brutality in Ukraine. They are not connected to any Azov movements anymore. It is true, that in the past they have overacted in the fight with Yanukovich bloody regime, and 6 years after they know where the border of action ends.<br />\n<br />\nThey assured us they are really against nazism and another kind of alt-right ideology. Their views are close to be right and very pro-Ukrainian, but it does not mean something bad. A lot of people were disappointed by the tattoos of these guys. They explained that all symbols are from Slavic paganism, traditionally used in the times of Kyiv Rus. The religion could be comparable with Japanese Shinto. Currently, they are representing the sport-social group &ldquo;Gonor&rdquo; and are huge football fans.<br />\n<br />\nThe visit to Hong Kong aimed just to see by own eyes the true what is going on there. During the Winter on fire, a lot of foreigners visited Kyiv to see the truth, and it is the same matter. It is not more than a touristic visit.<br />\n<br />\nGuys have recognized they have a specific style and a quite scaring look. But it is not a reason to call them nazi or to blame due to the tattoos.<br />\n<br />\nRegarding the twit with some provoking old pics, it is what we are calling the Russian point of view since for Putin Ukraine is full of radicals. As a result, after the twit, they started to get a lot of death threats on Facebook. Unfortunately, even Western journalists could become victims of Kremlin propaganda.<br />\n<br />\nWe are asking do not to follow fake news and provocations against Ukrainians.<br />\n<br />\nFirst of all, since these people are aiming just to know more about Hong Kong. And secondary, because all of us have a right to enjoy the freedom of travel as well as other civil liberties.<br />\n<br />\nNB: we tried to highlight the position of Gonor, which is not the position of FHKC.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wzj9X6h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwzj9X6h.png&h=428e8afb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95eb539b7e633b7146cafa27c953e35a8e44fbed","tid":1766711,"uid":65210,"like":91,"dislike":3,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T20:55:52.000Z","msg":"知錯能改 炒車就認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不完美可改善"},{"pid":"2150e06bafa4895f50c5c021d162af71e6aa51f5","tid":1766711,"uid":79724,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T20:56:11.000Z","msg":"總之長話短說就係賀幾位烏克蘭嘅前民兵嚟香港視察　&mdash;＞　總之長話短說就係<span style=\"color: red;\">*有</span>幾位烏克蘭嘅前民兵嚟香港視察"},{"pid":"ac690c88f82d65c353de858e8dfbf5ded9135741","tid":1766711,"uid":321674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T20:57:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2ab67cf2c86553f51eeff976aea06dae26cbcd8","tid":1766711,"uid":119325,"like":43,"dislike":39,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T20:57:52.000Z","msg":"下次打開你隻鳩眼先post文<br />\n豬閪衝出黎柒 哂鳩大家時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass